metadata.name: Gentle Breeze
metadata.description:
"Gentle Breeze"/ 青雲 Qingyun

The remnants of the flowers fade away and tiny green apricots grow on the treetops. 
Swallows are flying in the sky and clear rivers surround village homes. 
The willow branches have been blown less and less, but don't worry - lush and fragrant grass is visible everywhere.

ーーー
蘇軾 Su Shi. 《蝶戀花·春景》. Song dynasty.
